Project lineage (prior open-cfmoto forks studied / built upon)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

OpenCfMoto builds on research and code from the following open-cfmoto forks. At
the time of writing these repositories did not ship an explicit LICENSE file;
this project treats the shared AGPLv3 heritage of the Android Auto code as
governing and credits the prior authors here:

  * coletz / dcoletto  — dcoletto/open-cfmoto  (base app, QR/EasyConn work)
  * richardbizik        — richardbizik/open-cfmoto  (1000MT-X support)
  * BojanJ              — BojanJ/open-cfmoto  (Android Auto receiver integration)

